  "this site’s AI content rights policy": "የዚህ ድረ-ገጽ AI ይዘት መብቶች ፖሊሲ",
  "this site’s license catalog": "የዚህ ድረ-ገጽ የፈቃድ ካታሎግ",
  "training / fine_tuning / distillation — model internalization tiers": "training / fine_tuning / distillation — የሞዴል ውህደት ደረጃዎች",
